import React from 'react'
import './LoginScreen.css'

import LogoLateral from './LogoLateral'
import Login from './Login'

// eslint-disable-next-line import/no-anonymous-default-export
export default () => {
    return(
        <body>
            <section>
                <LogoLateral />
            </section>
            <aside>
                <Login />
            </aside>
        </body>
    )
}
